{"tid":561520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫】墨丸鯁喉女生 搶救26日不治","createTime":"2018-02-15T05:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T05:30:46.000Z","uid":124537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f82024b9a6140ea69b09c0785ac6cb1b6b35b4d","tid":561520,"uid":124537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180214/57831953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831953&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9bc2df8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831953&h=872712bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180214/57831953</a><br />\n<br />\n8歲小三女生，上月在元朗學校小食部食墨魚丸時鯁喉( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Bd7aaG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Bd7aaG&d=%2Ff3dVIMZAgN3cVdO%2BLpXNG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=133e06d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Bd7aaG</a> )，留院搶救26日後，於前日(周一)不治。<br />\n<br />\n女童姓周，於在元朗欖口村路佛教陳榮根紀念學校讀書。周父接受《蘋果》查詢時不欲多談，只語帶哀傷道：「心情還可以」，又指事件是意外，未有考慮追究。他透露從醫生得知女兒事發時因喉嚨鯁墨丸，造成腦部缺氧22分鐘，引致昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n他又指前日收到醫生的通知，趕住醫院，並非家人決定拔喉，但死亡原因有待確認。他對外界的關心表示感謝，但指目前不希望多談。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上月18日，女童於小息時間在小食部購買墨魚丸進食，期間鯁喉暈倒，送院搶救。留院期間，女童的父母每日也到兒童深切治療部探望女兒，愁眉不展。周父做財務策劃，於女兒出事後停工。他曾表示意外沒人想發生，因此沒有怪責學校。<br />\n<br />\n至於學校小食部，在事件後即時停售丸類，直至另行決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}